@page
@model IndexModel
@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Home page";
}

<div class="text-center mb-5">
    <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-primary">The .NET Solution Stack</h1>
    <p class="lead text-muted">Powering Group 6's Phase 1 Technical Implementation</p>
</div>

<div class="row g-4">
    <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="main-container h-100">
            <h2 class="h4 mb-3 border-bottom pb-2">Why .NET?</h2>
            <p>
                Our group decided to choose the .NET stack due to the balance of performance, security, and long-term maintainability. 
                Since .NET uses C# across much of the development process, it allows us to work more efficiently without having to switch between multiple languages or frameworks. 
                In addition, .NET integrates well with Microsoft Azure and other enterprise tools, which can simplify deployment and cloud management. 
                Its built-in security features and large developer community also make it a reliable choice for creating scalable and professional applications.
            </p>
            <ul class="list-unstyled mt-3">
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success"></i> <strong></strong> </li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success"></i> <strong></strong> </li>
                <li><i class="bi bi-check-circle-fill text-success"></i> <strong></strong> </li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-lg-6">
        <div class="main-container h-100">
            <h2 class="h4 mb-3 border-bottom pb-2">Technical Core</h2>
            <p>For Phase 1, our implementation focuses on the frontend and routing capabilities of the stack:</p>
            <table class="table table-sm mt-2">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>Layer</th>
                        <th>Technology</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td><strong>Frontend</strong></td>
                        <td>Razor Pages, Bootstrap, CSS</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <p>For Phase 2, our implementation focuses on an API that will go with the theme of what our website will be about. 
                We choose a free to play game to go with the origins of the group OASIS.
            </p>
            <table class="table table-sm mt-2">
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>
                            API
                        </th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <tb>Free to play Games</tb>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>